name: Lastmile Services Master Update
query:
SELECT
    name AS "LMS ID:Link/Lastmile Services Master:180",
    circuit_id AS "Circuit ID:Data:150",
    customer AS "Customer:Link/Customer:180",
    site AS "Site Name:Link/Site:180",
    supplier AS "Supplier:Link/Supplier:180",
    territory AS "Territory:Link/Territory:150",
    lms_stage AS "LMS Stage:Data:150",
    expected_delivery_date AS "Expected Delivery Date:Date:140",
    lms_delivery_date AS "LMS Delivery Date:Date:140",
    supplier_contact AS "Supplier Contact:Link/Contact:180",
    suppliernumber AS "Supplier Number:Data:130",
    email_address AS "Email Address:Data:200",
    lms_review AS "LMS Review:Data:250"    
FROM `tabLastmile Services Master`
ORDER BY creation DESC;
